n Villasa, ETA-2, Greater Noida, with 1075 sqft area. Enjoy 24/7 security, power backup, water supply, clubhouse, rainwater harvesting, and lush green areas.', '2BHK flat Greater Noida, Migsun Villasa ETA-2, 1075 sqft 2BHK Greater Noida, Greater Noida 2BHK amenities, flats with security Greater Noida', '0', '0', '1', NULL, '2024-11-13 06:27:07', '2024-11-28 16:05:07'),
