(1, 2, 'ELDECO RESIDENCY GREENS', 'uploads/subcategories/banner/VP3487aMJmqmkCdsbaZVHHydVj115u5D576K3dGp.jpg', NULL, '0', '0', 'eldeco-resedency-greens-in-greater-noida-flats', 'Discover premium flats for sale in Eldeco Residency Greens, Greater Noida, with options from 2 BHK to spacious 4 BHK + G layouts. Find your ideal home with Greater Noida Flats.', '<p>Eldeco Residency Greens in Greater Noida offers a selection of flats designed for comfortable living. Explore 2 BHK, 2 BHK + Study, 3 BHK, 4 BHK, and 4 BHK + G configurations, ideal for families and investors. Whether you\'re buying or selling, Greater Noida Flats connects you with the best options for modern, luxurious flats in this prestigious community.</p>', 'Eldeco Residency Greens Flats for Sale in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Buy or Sell Flats in Eldeco Residency Greens, Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Looking to buy or sell flats in Eldeco Residency Greens, Greater Noida? Greater Noida Flats offers premium listings from 2 BHK to 4 BHK + G units in this elite residential community.', 'Eldeco Residency Greens Greater Noida, Buy Flats Eldeco Residency Greens, Sell Flats Eldeco Residency Greens, 2 BHK to 4 BHK Flats Greater Noida, Greater Noida Flats', '1', NULL, '2024-10-26 02:20:26', '2024-12-04 04:27:34'),
(2, 2, 'MIGSUN ULTIMO', 'uploads/subcategories/banner/tfThripsVdSD7Z9JcpkQp3sXDc9lpNhaDWmZoNCD.jpg', NULL, '0', '0', 'migsun-ultimo-in-greater-noida-flats', 'Discover a range of spacious flats for sale in Migsun Ultimo, Greater Noida. Find your perfect fit with options from 2 BHK to 4 BHK + Servant, exclusively at Greater Noida Flats', '<p>Migsun Ultimo in Greater Noida offers a diverse selection of flats to meet various lifestyle needs. Available configurations include 695 sqft 2 BHK, 845 sqft 2 BHK, 1005 sqft 2 BHK, and 1150 sqft 2 BHK + Study for compact comfort. Larger layouts include 995 sqft, 1300 sqft, and 1395 sqft 3 BHK options, as well as a spacious 1595 sqft 3 BHK + Study. For those needing extra space, Migsun Ultimo also features a 2600 sqft 4 BHK + Servant option. Greater Noida Flats connects buyers and sellers with prime real estate opportunities in this sought-after community.</p>', 'Migsun Ultimo Flats for Sale in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Buy or Sell Flats in Migsun Ultimo, Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Explore flats for sale in Migsun Ultimo, Greater Noida, ranging from 2 BHK to 4 BHK + Servant. Greater Noida Flats is your trusted partner for buying or selling quality properties.', 'Migsun Ultimo Greater Noida, Buy Flats Migsun Ultimo, Sell Flats Migsun Ultimo, 2 BHK to 4 BHK Flats Greater Noida, Flats for Sale Greater Noida, Greater Noida Flats', '1', NULL, '2024-10-26 02:35:45', '2024-12-04 04:26:58'),
(3, 2, 'UNITECH HORIZON', 'uploads/subcategories/banner/RUiE2ATgBowpnBTqzb5wY1mKVCpbau327X0d7tLE.jpg', NULL, '0', '0', 'unitech-horizon-in-greater-noida-flats', 'Explore spacious 3 BHK flats for sale in Unitech Horizon, Greater Noida, exclusively listed with Greater Noida Flats.', '<p>Unitech Horizon in Greater Noida offers spacious 3 BHK flats, ideal for families or investors seeking quality living. With options such as the 1746 sqft and 1768 sqft 3 BHK layouts, these flats provide ample space, modern amenities, and a prime location. Greater Noida Flats is your trusted platform for buying or selling flats in Unitech Horizon, ensuring a seamless experience in the Greater Noida real estate market.</p>', 'Unitech Horizon Flats for Sale in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Buy or Sell 3 BHK Flats in Unitech Horizon, Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Discover 3 BHK flats for sale in Unitech Horizon, Greater Noida, with spacious layouts of 1746 and 1768 sqft. Greater Noida Flats offers premier listings for buying or selling.', 'Unitech Horizon Greater Noida, Buy Flats Unitech Horizon, Sell Flats Unitech Horizon, 3 BHK Flats Greater Noida, Flats for Sale Greater Noida, Greater Noida Flats', '1', NULL, '2024-10-26 02:46:09', '2024-12-04 04:26:37'),
(4, 2, 'STELLAR MI CITIHOMES', 'uploads/subcategories/banner/UbFkNA4uKBiDzzVtwK2zIY100vgZXdPLRSUxuSaX.jpg', NULL, '0', '0', 'stellar-mi-citihomes-in-greater-noida-flats', 'Find quality 2 BHK flats for sale in Stellar MI Citihomes, Greater Noida, with exclusive listings on Greater Noida Flats.', '<p>Stellar MI Citihomes in Greater Noida offers well-designed 2 BHK flats, perfect for modern living. With options such as the 1110 sqft and 1164 sqft 2 BHK layouts, these flats combine comfort and functionality in a prime location. Greater Noida Flats connects buyers and sellers with the best listings in Stellar MI Citihomes, making it easy to find or sell your ideal home in Greater Noida.</p>', 'Stellar MI Citihomes Flats for Sale in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Buy or Sell 2 BHK Flats in Stellar MI Citihomes, Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Discover 2 BHK flats for sale in Stellar MI Citihomes, Greater Noida, with layouts of 1110 and 1164 sqft. Greater Noida Flats is your trusted source for buying or selling in this vibrant community.', 'Stellar MI Citihomes Greater Noida, Buy Flats Stellar MI Citihomes, Sell Flats Stellar MI Citihomes, 2 BHK Flats Greater Noida, Flats for Sale Greater Noida, Greater Noida Flats', '1', NULL, '2024-10-26 02:51:29', '2024-12-04 04:25:47'),
(5, 2, 'SDS NRI RESIDENCY', 'uploads/subcategories/banner/55Khhf8rrJjAPjPhQq7X4HVUeHpF38r56zSuqMeF.jpg', NULL, '0', '0', 'sds--nri-residency-in-greater-noida-flats', 'Explore exclusive 1BHK to 4+Study flats at SDS NRI Residency in Greater Noida, available for buying and selling through Greater Noida Flats.', '<p>Greater Noida Flats presents SDS NRI Residency, offering premium flats tailored to every lifestyle, from compact 1BHKs (660 sq. ft.) to expansive 4+Study options (2400 sq. ft.). Perfectly designed for comfort and functionality, these flats are ideal for individuals and families looking to invest in or sell top-notch properties in Greater Noida. Available layouts include 1BHK at 660 sq. ft., 2+Study at 1259 sq. ft., 3BHK at 1359 sq. ft., 4BHK at 1659 sq. ft., and 4+Study options at 2100 and 2400 sq. ft.</p>', 'SDS NRI Residency Flats for Sale in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Buy or Sell SDS NRI Residency Flats in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Discover SDS NRI Residency flats in Greater Noida. Buy or sell 1BHK to 4+Study flats with Greater Noida Flats for a smooth and reliable experience.', 'SDS NRI Residency Flats Greater Noida, Buy or Sell Flats SDS NRI Residency, Flats in Greater Noida, Greater Noida Flats', '1', NULL, '2024-10-26 03:00:00', '2024-12-04 04:25:18'),
(6, 2, 'KENDRIYA VIHAR CWHO', 'uploads/subcategories/banner/iXhVrTYs1VudBWdwxpUhXbIxysSmlUEdTnvXFfgK.jpg', NULL, '0', '0', 'kendriya-vihar-cwho-in-greater-noida-flats', 'Discover 1BHK to 4BHK flats at Kendriya Vihar CWHO in Greater Noida, available for buying and selling with Greater Noida Flats.', '<p>Greater Noida Flats offers a range of flats at Kendriya Vihar CWHO, ideal for buyers and sellers in Greater Noida. With thoughtfully designed spaces, these flats suit various preferences, including 1BHKs at 675 sq. ft., 2BHKs at 1123 sq. ft., 3BHKs at 1450 sq. ft., and spacious 4BHKs at 2100 sq. ft. Whether investing or selling, explore quality living spaces that balance comfort and convenience at Kendriya Vihar CWHO.</p>', 'Kendriya Vihar CWHO Flats for Sale in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Buy or Sell Kendriya Vihar CWHO Flats in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Explore flats at Kendriya Vihar CWHO in Greater Noida, ranging from 1BHK to 4BHK. Buy or sell through Greater Noida Flats for a smooth property experience.', 'Kendriya Vihar CWHO Flats Greater Noida, Buy or Sell Flats Kendriya Vihar CWHO, Flats in Greater Noida, Greater Noida Flats', '1', NULL, '2024-10-26 03:04:29', '2024-12-04 04:24:53'),
(7, 2, 'MIGSUN TWINZ', 'uploads/subcategories/banner/oBm559lAFHgQ04kNlfNa56Kf2oWu3N9xwaShAD04.jpg', NULL, '0', '0', 'migsun-twinz-in-greater-noida-flats', 'Explore 2BHK to 4BHK flats at Migsun Twinz in Greater Noida, available for buying and selling through Greater Noida Flats.', '<p>Greater Noida Flats features Migsun Twinz, a premium choice for 2BHK to 4BHK flats in Greater Noida, designed for those seeking quality and convenience. Ranging from cozy 2BHKs at 697 and 845 sq. ft. to spacious 3BHKs at 995 and 1399 sq. ft., and extending up to 4BHKs at 1595 sq. ft., Migsun Twinz offers options that cater to various lifestyle needs. Perfect for buyers and sellers, this property is ideal for comfortable living and a sound investment in Greater Noida.</p>', 'Migsun Twinz Flats for Sale in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Buy or Sell Migsun Twinz Flats in Greater Noida | Greater Noida Flats', 'Find 2BHK to 4BHK flats at Migsun Twinz in Greater Noida. Buy or sell with Greater Noida Flats for a seamless property experience.', 'Migsun Twinz Flats Greater Noida, Buy or Sell Flats Migsun Twinz, Flats in Greater Noida, Greater Noida Flats', '1', NULL, '2024-10-26 03:09:43', '2024-12-04 04:24:31'),
